{
  "id": "foundry-mcp-bridge",
  "title": "Foundry MCP Bridge",
  "description": "Connect Foundry VTT to AI models through MCP protocol. Enable AI-powered actor creation, intelligent compendium search, campaign analysis, and interactive dice roll coordination. Adds combat play-by-play, a live chat-log buffer, in-character chat, resource/spell-slot tracking, active-effect & condition management, an initiative/turn tracker, token positioning & distance measurement, and a persistent session event log. Supports Claude, local LLMs, and future AI models with comprehensive GM-only security.",
